des:
Ask for dog Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dogs.

Dog Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

This is a very simple skill mainly made for learning purposes.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch dog Facts" or "Alexa, open dog Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
